text: Unaporanga lanceolata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 2007. It is known from Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Unaporanga lanceolata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2007
